makefile: make all to compile objects and executables

udp_client: Usage: ./udp_client <ipv4 address> <port>, sends default message
			on given port to given ip addr.

udp_server: Usage: ./udp_server <ipv4 address> <port>, listens on given port
			until udp packet recieved, then returns packet to client.

fancy_client: Usage: ./fancy_client <ipv4 address> <port>, requests user string
			  input in loop until success, sends string to port at given ip,
			  waits for response and prints to stdout.
